==English==
===Noun===
'''[[pronominal]] [[adverb]]'''
# a type of adverb occurring in a number of Germanic languages, formed in replacement of a preposition and a pronoun by turning the latter into a locative adverb and the former into an prepositional adverb and joining them in reverse order. 
#: '''For''' ''that'' => [[therefore|''there'''''fore''']]
#: '''By''' ''this'' => [[hereby|''here'''''by''']]
#: '''In''' ''what'' => [[wherein|''where'''''in''']]

